    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Outdoor Recreation Enhancement Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 to extend the exemption from minimum wage and maximum hours requirements to an employee of a recreational establishment engaged in providing services or facilities directly related to outfitting and guiding or similar outdoor recreation activities, or rental of outdoor recreational equipment.</p> <p>And federal agency shall notify the holder of any contract, permit, license, or other agreement with the agency of this exemption for these employees.</p>]]></text>
